Name: hemochromatosis type 2A
Definition: A hemochromatosis type 2 that has_material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the HJV gene on chromosome 1q21.

Name: hemochromatosis type 2B
Definition: A hemochromatosis type 2 that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the HAMP gene on chromosome 19q13.
